@TheLightWell   I am a movie fanatic and I haven't been to the movies since 2016.  I just want to be a good ally to the marginalized Perma-Victims of the USA by not subjecting the movie theaters to my inherently oppressive white maleness.
The theater then becomes a safe space where people can heal from "generational trauma."
The sad thing is that I won't be able to enjoy the thrilling spectacle of all the *awesome* Empowering Girl Boss movies that the Hollywood DEI community is churning out.  The sight of a woman being perfect at everything and throwing men around like rag dolls never gets old.
